Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:02.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect memorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:07.36,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index apparently used 85% of her brain's capacity to memorize 103,000 grimoires.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:13.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Since she can only use the remaining 15%, she needs to have her memories erased every year or else she'll die...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:14.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...said the magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:16.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And only three days remain until that limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:19.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I was out cold for three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:27.69,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(1158,493)}#05 Limit\NMidnight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:25.61,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Kamijyo-chan, Sensei's going out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:30.43,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,I might be back late,\Nso take care of the house while I'm away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:12.90,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't hurt Touma anymore!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:23.36,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,There's twelve hours and thirty-eight minutes left until the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:27.64,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to see the effect of the "fetter"\Ndepending on whether you chose to escape or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.17,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,but this exceeds our expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:30.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Fetter...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:36.55,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want us to take away that "toy",\Nthen I suggest you throw away the idea of escaping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.59,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:47.41,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:54.56,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,If I negotiate with them,\Nyour daily life won't get altered any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.28,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let them step any further into your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:00.96,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...so it's... all-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:22.26,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.32,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:29.98,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Kanzaki... was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:33.49,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to know each other's names.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.92,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Is she... is Index there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Must I wake her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:41.36,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:43.40,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Listen as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:46.75,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The limit is tonight at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:53.64,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We are preparing our schedule to finish everything to match that exact time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:56.17,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:00.18,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've told me,\Ndon't you think I'd resist until the very end?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:03.60,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need some time for farewells?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:07.21,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,This is neither a conversation nor a negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:08.45,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:13.74,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Bid her farewell before we arrive and leave that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:18.40,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,All of you are pushing your own incompetence on others...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:20.61,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are magicians, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Will magic really not solve anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:28.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Won't Index be able to find a solution using her 103,000 grimoires?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:31.50,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Of everything, the Church fears\Na rebellion from Index the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:38.41,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,There are most likely biases amongst those grimoires,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:42.70,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,such as, she is not allowed to learn anything related to Mind Hound. {orig. novel term for memory manipulation}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, your own magic can't solve anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:51.81,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,There is a fear magicians outside of Necessarius would dispel environments created by magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.64,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way the Church would allow such possibilities to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:04:02.38,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,And most importantly, the act of memorizing grimoires itself signifies the contamination of the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You guys knowingly let Index...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.87,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We were only informed afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.43,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Magic... won't solve anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What about... us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:18.71,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:20.56,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The science side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:24.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We have many methods of scientifically removing people's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:29.12,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We could have a solution you don't have that could remove the 103,000 grimoires from her brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.61,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Academy City!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:34.55,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of espers that can control one's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:37.15,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to give up all hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:45.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still going to give up trying or challenging things\Nand put someone's life at risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:49.09,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,These are cheap words for persuading your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:56.00,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,If you look at it from our side,\Nat least we have successfully saved her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:05:00.35,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,We do not trust your bet that has nothing to support itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.22,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that this is neither trying nor challenging,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.61,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,but rather, just, recklessness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:12.81,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, there is no place for a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.74,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll crush you, arch-rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:22.07,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save her and steal all the heroic moments for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:27.28,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,If she collapses again, consider it too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.36,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,See you at midnight, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:32.22,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,There really is little time remaining...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:36.33,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Show us a sensational struggle to the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:01.86,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Memory loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:06.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Loss of memory due to aging is one kind of memory loss,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:10.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the loss of memory caused by the stoppage of blood to the brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:20.77,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Loss of memory from side effects of halothane, isoflurane, general anesthesia, or benzodiazepine, same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting anywhere like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.63,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Cellphone bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:30.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:36.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just ask Komoe-sensei to introduce me to\Na neurological research or mental ability institute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing, Komoe-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:50.24,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'll just have to call random places...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:15.46,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:35.51,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.54,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect memorization?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.34,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.58,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,But, you need to tell me the symptoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.28,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.11,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,What time of the day do you think it is right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.20,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost midnight, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.93,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.14,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.73,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:03.00,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.49,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:54.95,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.35,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Refer to Moonchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.67,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have an angel descend and create its temple in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.86,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to kill her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.59,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:20.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's 1,800,000 espers in this Academy City...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and more than one thousand research facilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:27.83,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to those places, we might not have to use this last resort!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.60,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't want to use this method either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:35.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're hoping that there's some other way deep inside your heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then wait a bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:44.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a way to resolve this so that everyone is smiling and happy in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.14,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.21,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.04,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Can you spit out the same words in front of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:56.34,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,A person who has fought against this all her life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:59.48,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,A patient who can't even open her eyes because of all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:02.10,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell her to wait a bit because you want to try some stuff out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:07.40,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,To let doctors whose name and face are unknown... to let them play around with her body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.04,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,...and let her waste away with drugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.50,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,...that's not something a human can come up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.03,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.87,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still human?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:18.38,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Or a monster that quit being human?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.68,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,This is an artifact necessary for removing her memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.38,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,a magic ornament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:29.19,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Touch it with your right hand,\Nand that should be enough to dispel its magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.85,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,We're just killing her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.30,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,She'll still have her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:40.07,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,But if your trials fail, she will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.29,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,So can you still do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.37,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,In front of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:47.54,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still take this away in front of a girl in that much pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.85,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,If you trust your abilities that much, then do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:52.99,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You blasted mutant that thinks of yourself as a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:56.35,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.59,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be grateful if you could help me fill up my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:05.37,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,The ritual will begin at 12:15 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.76,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,We will borrow the powers of Leo to kill her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:09.83,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:23.13,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say my final goodbye to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:26.55,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a single second to spare for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:29.16,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind just disappearing from here, monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.06,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Your right hand took out my flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.99,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't understand the principle behind it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:41.63,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want any single thing to influence the ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.14,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:51.33,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I even have the ability to save one girl in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.34,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,There's about ten minutes before the start of the ritual, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:06.57,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The night when we swore to erase her memories for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:09.37,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,we wept next to her the entire night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.38,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,B-But!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:15.90,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know what this guy's gonna do in his current state!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.68,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,What if this guy tries to commit a double suicide the second we let our eyes off him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:22.99,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think he would've touched the cross already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:27.10,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It is exactly because we have\Nconfirmed him to still be human
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.06,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,that you wanted to test him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.08,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:33.97,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, the ritual won't begin until the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:36.72,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,If he still has regrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:41.05,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,then there is a danger that we will have obstacles during the ritual, Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.48,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You have ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:48.19,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.66,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Tou...ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:08.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:18.20,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, there seems to be a formation in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:20.07,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Something about a regeneration magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.13,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Magic... whose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.51,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Those magicians came again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.73,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, you need to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now, Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:34.86,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.50,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:42.05,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.20,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever lose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Those people that treat you this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:53.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick every one of their butts, that's how strong I'll become...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.15,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:56.64,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll save you all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.92,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:03.94,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:20.38,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow this worst kind of ending, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.51,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:30.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't do anything about the 103,000 grimoires that occupy 85% of her brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:36.53,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,nor could I protect the one-year's worth of memories inside the remaining 15%.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:45.41,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,85% of her brain is allocated to the 103,000 grimoires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:50.24,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,That is why she can only use 15% of a normal person's brain capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.99,Default,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Memory erasure takes place in exact one year periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:02.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why can she only live for one year with 15% of her brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.97,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No, even before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:11.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...how did Kanzaki get to numbers like 85% or 15%?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.46,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:17.83,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that must be your voice, Kamijyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:22.06,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be using Sensei's phone without her permission, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.76,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, perfect memorization?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:32.30,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is a rare case, but that by itself is just a physical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:37.53,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And will one use up 15% of a brain's capacity in one year?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:44.25,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it's a miserable physical condition where one's brain breaks down around the age of six to seven, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:51.13,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that people with perfect memorization can't forget the single smallest thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:54.89,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,but one's brain definitely won't break down because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:16:00.01,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,A human's brain can store 140 years worth of memories to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for a human brain to break down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:11.90,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,We just don't have one place for memories to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:15.75,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,We have semantic memory,\Nwhich governs language and knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:18.97,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,We have procedural memory,\Nwhich governs the know-how of your motor functions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:22.20,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, we have episodal memory,\Nwhich governs your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:23.37,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.28,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's plenty of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.49,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.28,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, umm... Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:34.17,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, no matter how much knowledge you force into the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:37.61,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,it won't create so much pressure that the brain blows open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.93,Default,Komoe,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible, at least, in neurology~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:50.59,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index's perfect memorization isn't a life-threatening condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:54.80,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That would mean that the Church lied to Kanzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why is Index in pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The Church messed with Index's brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:06.83,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...and made it so that she would die\Nif her memories weren't killed in one-year periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:12.80,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That way, Index, who possesses 103,000 grimoires, would never betray them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:18.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,That way, Index's friends will have to swallow their tears and obey them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:22.93,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But what exactly did the Church do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:29.35,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,If you trust your abilities that much, then do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.50,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You blasted mutant that pretends to be a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not pretending to be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I will become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's happening, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.21,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not touching anything supernatural?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:19.43,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, is there any place I haven't touched yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.05,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.11,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 3, Verse 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:22.09,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Confirmed the penetration of seals 1 to 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.70,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Preparing to regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:24.96,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.90,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Auto-regeneration cannot be carried out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:29.78,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Presently, in order to protect the library of 103,000 grimoires,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:32.83,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,prioritizing engaging with the intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:39.50,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse engineering the magic formula that destroyed the barriers, based on the 103,000 grimoires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.50,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.97,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,No applicable spell found.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:48.20,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Forcing the disclosure of the spell's composition and constructing a local weapon against the intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.39,0:19:55.15,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Successfully constructed the most effective weapon against the intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:20:00.03,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Now initiating local weapon, "St. George's Sanctuary".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.08,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Proceeding to destroy intruder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.97,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.27,0:20:27.00,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,St. George's Sanctuary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.58,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...has created an infinite amount of distance between me and Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,But just one more step...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:32.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,...if I can just take one more step...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely reach her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.86,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Imagine Breaker".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.62,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,this epic will begin!
